HOW-TO Add a chart (new API)

 Adding charts to your report is quite simple. Supported charts are:
 
 * Area
  
 * Bar
 
 * Bar 3D

 * Line
 
 * Pie
 
 * Pie 3D
 
 * Scatter
 
 * Stacked area

 * Stacked bar

 * Stacked bar 3D
 
 * Time series
 
 * XY area

 * XY bar

 * XY line
 
 []
 
*How charts work

 Like you would do using a spreadsheet (like OpenOffice or Excel) were you have flat data (ie: column1, column2, column3)
 and you want to make a chart with column1 and column3, you need to tell which column is going to be used as series/categories
 and which column we are going to operate (sum, average, count, distinct count, etc).  

 Depending of the type of chart you want to add, you'll have to use its proper builder, there is one builder per type because
 they have so many different options, that it would be very confusing and not intuitive to have all possible options in the same builder.
 
